{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5",
    "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
    "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
    "chapterNumber": 5,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Thessalonians 5 in Church Slavonic (Elizabeth Bible)."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.1",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:1",
      "text": "А о летех и о временех, братие, не требе есть вам писати,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.2",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:2",
      "text": "сами бо вы известно весте, яко день Господень, якоже тать в нощи, тако приидет.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.3",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:3",
      "text": "Егда бо рекут: мир и утверждение, тогда внезапу нападет на них всегубительство, якоже болезнь во чреве имущей, и не имут избежати.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.4",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:4",
      "text": "Вы же, братие, несте во тме, да день вас якоже тать постигнет:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.5",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:5",
      "text": "вси бо вы сынове света есте: и сынове дне: несмы нощи, ниже тьмы.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.6",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:6",
      "text": "Темже убо да не спим, якоже и прочии, но да бодрствуим и трезвимся.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.7",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:7",
      "text": "Спящии бо, в нощи спят, и упивающиися в нощи упиваются.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.8",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:8",
      "text": "Мы же, сынове суще дне, да трезвимся, оболкшеся в броню веры и любве и шлем упования спасения,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.9",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:9",
      "text": "яко не положи нас Бог в гнев, но в получение спасения Господем нашим Иисус Христом,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.10",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:10",
      "text": "умершим за нас, да, аще бдим, аще ли спим, купно с Ним живем.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.11",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:11",
      "text": "Сего ради утешайте друг друга, и созидайте кийждо ближняго, якоже и творите.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.12",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:12",
      "text": "Молим же вы, братие, знайте труждающихся у вас, и настоятелей ваших о Господе, и наказующих вы,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.13",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:13",
      "text": "и имейте их по преизлиха в любви за дело их: мирствуйте в себе.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.14",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:14",
      "text": "Молим же вы, братие, вразумляйте безчинныя, утешайте малодушныя, заступайте немощныя, долготерпите ко всем.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.15",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:15",
      "text": "Блюдите, да никтоже зла за зло кому воздаст: но всегда доброе гоните и друг ко другу и ко всем.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.16",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:16",
      "text": "Всегда радуйтеся.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.17",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:17",
      "text": "Непрестанно молитеся.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.18",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:18",
      "text": "О всем благодарите: сия бо есть воля Божия о Христе Иисусе в вас.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.19",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:19",
      "text": "Духа не угашайте.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.20",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:20",
      "text": "Пророчествия не уничижайте.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.21",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:21",
      "text": "Вся же искушающе, добрая держите.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.22",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:22",
      "text": "От всякия вещи злыя огребайтеся.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.23",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:23",
      "text": "Сам же Бог мира да освятит вас всесовершенных во всем: и всесовершен ваш дух и душа и тело непорочно в пришествие Господа нашего Иисуса Христа да сохранится.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.24",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:24",
      "text": "Верен Призвавый вас, Иже и сотворит.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.25",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:25",
      "text": "Братие, молитеся о нас.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.26",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:26",
      "text": "Целуйте братию всю лобзанием святым.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.27",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:27",
      "text": "Заклинаю вы Господем, прочести послание сие пред всею святою братиею.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "cu-elizabeth:first-thessalonians.5.28",
      "translationId": "cu-elizabeth",
      "bookSlug": "first-thessalonians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Thessalonians 5:28",
      "text": "Благодать Господа нашего Иисуса Христа с вами. Аминь.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
